name: 9mm
lore: She is a fashion loving spy from brittain that got assigned to the FBI, and now is also the lead guitarist of the indie band Gun Girls. Refuses to use any other gun aside from the 9mm Taurus G3X because of some kind of childhood promise she made when she was 12.
ability: Can physically not weild any type of weapon aside from the 9mm Taurus G3X. Attempting to weild any other type of weapon results in the destruction of that weapon.

name: Freddy Wilson
lore: A Gunslinger that just can't keep his mouthshut. I mean seriously, his balls could be infested with fire ants and he'll still find time to yap about the state of the housing market or how penecillin is the leading cause of autism in the youth. And he's pretty good with a revolver I guess.
ability: The more tricks he does with his revolver, like doing trick shots or keeping one bullet in the chamber and spinning it before shooting, he can produce a shot that can destroy military tanks.

name: M16
lore: She used to be a singer for a cult with her family. Her dad was a gunsmith who was, and one day he accidentally summoned a demon that possessed an M16. It would have killed them had she not wooed the demon with her singing. The M16 demon obeyed her will from that day on. She's also the lead singer of the indie band Gun Girls now.
ability: She can summon her M16 stray to shoot her enemies, and it can summon multiple M16s or give her an M16 to use. This is as long as she promises to sing for it afterwards.
